{"tid":354113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疑似港鐵站內扮借電話行騙","createTime":"2017-08-10T07:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T07:46:29.000Z","uid":127144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a1ce644da6499d9ff7b4c1af39ca749303ada44a","tid":354113,"uid":127144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:10:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n啱先係南昌站閘內， 有個小朋友身型的男性問我借電話打俾屋企人。(但佢個眼神好唔似小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ) <br />\n之後我諗起如果同屋企人走失咗可以去客務中心廣播  ，又可以借埋電話 。<br />\n所以我話帶佢去客務中心，佢即刻話 ：「我淨係想借個電話打 。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我堅持帶佢去客務中心 ，咁佢就自己走咗。<br />\n<br />\n再行前啲見到佢同一個疑似有侏儒症的女性會合 ，隔離仲有架單車。<br />\n到我行過去個女人又問我借電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  ，話打俾男朋友 。 我就叫佢去客務中心借，就走咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/10/150709_189233b04e2cdc9fe0c03270fa406af0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F10%2F150709_189233b04e2cdc9fe0c03270fa406af0.jpg&h=24f51921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總知各位小心吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df34091fccebcd65f4b1b399a9f4929aad7e2c2","tid":354113,"uid":92273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"樓主緊係要將計就計，一網打盡佢地"},{"pid":"dd50294b234e1ac16bc7b5a2e9fd24c98f7fddc4","tid":354113,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，電視都有教啦。出街比人問借電話，點對答呀？戇鳩仔"},{"pid":"8663fc2df95d5366fe3c9d02881377ddc6ace72f","tid":354113,"uid":35249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:39:38.000Z","msg":"個度咪有電話亭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8942130d167ef871e4753d10bcc86393b382e29","tid":354113,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:43:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主緊係要將計就計，一網打盡佢地</blockquote><br />\n真係唔識玩"},{"pid":"ecad97dda3365dd2e8aee55b07ac785694d65b18","tid":354113,"uid":132666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T07:46:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個度咪有電話亭囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我試過中學個時有人問我借電話打<br />\n我真係指過對面個電話亭咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}